                                                                                                    Privacy Statement
                                                            </h1></div></div></div><div class="pt-content__container pt-content__container--static"><main class="pt-static-container"><div class="pt-static-content"><h3>Privacy Statement Coverage</h3><p>This is the official Privacy Statement of <a href="/" class="link">powerthesaurus.org</a> Website (Power Thesaurus). This
                Privacy Statement covers how Power Thesaurus treats personally identifiable information that Power Thesaurus
                collects and receives. This Privacy Statement does not apply to the practices of other companies that Power
                Thesaurus does not own or control.</p><p></p><p></p><h3>Personal Information Collection and Use</h3><p>You can read, browse and search for content on Power Thesaurus without having a Power Thesaurus account.</p><p>We may keep records about your usage of Power Thesaurus, including but not limited to, information on our
                server logs from your browser, your IP address, information you display or click on in Power Thesaurus,
                contacts you communicate with, opened correspondence and newsletters released and distributed by Power
                Thesaurus via e-mail and transactions with Power Thesaurus and our business partners. Additionally, Power
                Thesaurus may set and access cookies on your computer and allows other companies and entities that show
                advertisements on our pages to set and access their cookies on your computer; however other companies' use
                of their cookies is subject to their own privacy policies, not Power Thesaurus's Privacy Statement and other
                companies or entities do not have access to Power Thesaurus's cookies.</p><p>Power Thesaurus can use your personal information to customize the advertising and content you see on Power
                Thesaurus, improve quality of our design and services, create new features, monitor aggregate metrics,
                analyse preferences and trends for promotions, better features and Website's functionality, monitor the
                effectiveness of our marketing campaigns, contact you, conduct research and display targeted advertisements
                based on your personal information.</p><p>Power Thesaurus does not sell, rent or share your personally identifiable information with others except to
                provide services you have requested. Power Thesaurus does not use your personal information for commercial
                or marketing communication, except in cases where you will have the ability to opt-in or opt-out.</p><p>Nevertheless, Power Thesaurus may use your e-mail address at any time for non-marketing or administrative
                purposes, including but not limited to, new features or changes on Power Thesaurus.</p><p>Power Thesaurus can disclose and use your personally identifiable information to respond to subpoenas, court
                orders, or legal process, or to establish or exercise our legal rights or defend against legal claims.
                Additionally, we will disclose, use and share your personal information in order to examine, investigate,
                prevent, or take action regarding illicit or illegitimate activities, suspected fraud or scam, situations
                involving potential threats to the physical safety of any person, breach or infringement of Power
                Thesaurus's Terms and Conditions, or as otherwise required by laws of the United States or other country's,
                state's or territory's applicable jurisdiction. We have the right to transfer your personal information in
                the event of Power Thesaurus being acquired by or merged with another entity.</p><p>Personal information that you willingly and voluntarily disclose online becomes publicly available and can be
                viewed and used by others as permitted through functionality of the Website and under Power Thesaurus's <a
                        href="/_terms_conditions" class="link">Terms and Conditions</a>.</p><h3>Changes to Privacy Statement</h3><p>Power Thesaurus retains sole rights to alter or revise its Privacy Statement from time to time without any
                notice given to you, and you agree to be bound by such amendments or changes.</p><h3>Feedback and Questions</h3><p>If you have any questions, enquiries or feedback in relation to Power Thesaurus's Privacy Statement please
                sent us email to <a
                        href="mailto:privacy@powerthesaurus.org?subject=Enquiries" class="link" >privacy@powerthesaurus.org</a></p></div></main></div></div><footer class="pt-footer                     pt-footer--static                "><div class="pt-footer__wrapper pt-footer__wrapper--static"><div class="pt-footer__container pt-footer__container--static"><div class="pt-footer__links"><a href="/_about"
